channel.title: From the Depths of my Closet- DevoClean
channel.description:
[center][img]http://i42.tinypic.com/2a4sqza.png[/img][/center] DevoClean is an old ass server I was working on, gosh, nearly a year + ago. I recently found it on a thumbdrive along with a couple other servers I was working on in my closet upon cleaning it. [b]Not much[/b] is done/was done. Just releasing cause I have no further plans on it.
[b]Features:[/b] -Devo 7 Based -Around 10 Minor Bugs Fixed -Packaged, Clean -About 2 stability fixes, so it's slightly faster -Information.Java, allows changing of a few simple things. Can add more easily.
http://www.mediafire.com/?zmnlqmwgfzv
